title: You're Not An Adult Unless You Do THIS

author: Mark Manson
description:
For nearly 20 years, I’ve called out everything wrong with the self-help world. The bad science, the guru nonsense, and the advice that preys on people’s insecurities. But last year, I realized I could actually build something better. In this video, I reveal the project that pushed me out of criticizing the industry and into reinventing it: an AI designed to challenge you, understand you, and help you grow in ways traditional therapy and generic chatbots simply can’t.

This isn’t about feeling better, but about becoming better. And if we get this right, it could transform how millions of people find purpose, meaning, and real change in their lives. Let me show you what we’ve built and why I believe it’s the most important thing I’ve ever worked on.

Check it out here: https://purpose.app/bonus

If you are not already a member of my premium community, get access to monthly challenges and daily action steps that add up to real change here: https://mrk.mn/ZcFwvxv
